=== EVENT_WORMHOLE ===
# id: 30
# title: Wormhole Aperture
# chinese_title: 虫洞
# category: AnomalyEncounter
# mode: starmap

A stable wormhole shimmers ahead — an impossibility according to known physics. Sensors detect a habitable system on the other side.

* [Enter the wormhole]
  ~ gain_fuel(8)
  虫洞 (chóngdòng) — wormhole
* [Send a probe through first]
  ~ gain_credits(10)
  探针 (tànzhēn) — probe
* [This is too risky — go around]
  ~ lose_fuel(3)
  风险 (fēngxiǎn) — risk
